. This work uncovers\nfirst-time evidence of the manifestation of chromospheric intermediate shocks\nin sunspot umbrae, providing a new method for the potential thermalization of\nwave energy in a range of magnetic structures, including pores, magnetic flux\nropes, and magnetic bright points.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Feb 2020 19:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-08"}
