 good agreement with the\ndistance derived from a 3-dimensional photoionization modelling of Abell 14,\nindicating the presence of a binary system at the centre of the planetary\nnebula.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Feb 2020 19:00:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-02"}
