ons,\nincluding the Even-Mansour construction, the FX construction, some Sponge\nauthenticated modes of encryption, and many more.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Feb 2020 21:05:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-02"}
