on star PSR\nJ0737$-$3039, and the rediscovery of a bright radio pulsar originally found\nduring the first Molonglo pulsar surveys with an incorrectly catalogued\nposition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Feb 2020 23:41:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-06"}
